{
  "stem": "1975.3",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 15.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I remember that I was running like never in my life, you know.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And some bullets crossed my path, but I run.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And it was a very-- a corn field.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And run as fast as I was able to, and then I threw myself in the corn field in order to just lay for a little while.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And now that they have called this guy-- threw his bicycle apparently.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "First of all, he went to the guy to inquire the guy that he heard.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And apparently, they shot him.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "That's what we found out a little bit later.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And the other friends of mine, I just didn't know what actually happened.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "I know exactly what happened to me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "They have tried to search the area with horses, but, fortunately, there was also a luck, a little bit of luck, and, apparently, they have not spotted me.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "Otherwise, I wouldn't be here.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So then nighttime, I start moving a little bit farther.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I saw some flickering lights.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I start moving towards the flickering lights.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then I found myself in a little-- a little-- [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] forest.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then I prepared-- it was cold.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was, I think, April or May, and nighttime was very cold.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So what I did is I cut some grass with my hands.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And there was a little bit-- like in the river.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But very little river.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And this was gave me source.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I had my hat, and I used my hat to drink some water.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I was very hungry and I almost ate grass or something.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And then part of the grass, I used to keep that, and then I stayed there for a day.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Next day, I heard voices.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And the voices were in Russian.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
